      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──第7周的早晨。\n这周龙姐又联系了我。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（第7周了…和龙姐的关系变了不少。最近她在施术时的反应明显不一样了……）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "triggerWeeklySettlement": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（客源也很稳定……都是多亏了龙姐的介绍。照这样下去，债务也能慢慢还清了……）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……嗯。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "龙姐！今天也……等等，怎么了？看起来有点疲惫……"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "……没什么。就是有点没睡好。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "没睡好吗？上周也说睡不着来着……"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "……嗯。反正就是……还是睡不好。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "奇怪的梦还在继续做吗？",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "……嗯。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "……不如说，反而……更严重了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "更严重了……？",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "……早上醒来就一身汗……怎么说呢，身体莫名地发烫。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（来了……！完全是欲求不满的征兆啊。我的施术效果太好了……）",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "……还有，那个……内衣，就是……",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "内衣怎么了……？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "……早上醒来，莫名地……有点湿……",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（哇……真的假的。在梦里就到了……）",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "那个梦……是什么样的梦呢？",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "……！都说了不想讲了……",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "但是这对施术有参考价值……哪怕告诉我一点内容也好……",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "……。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "……梦里会出现你。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "text": "诶，我？"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（太好了……！完全陷进来了啊。龙姐居然对我……！）",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "在梦里，我在做什么呢？"
    },
