    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（被摸了……！）",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "摸了哪里……？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "所以说！不是说了别再问了吗！！",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（到底是什么样的梦呢……胸？还是……更下面？）",
      "hideCharacter": true
