    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "白天也会……吗？",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（白天也……？那工作的时候也会欲火焚身吗……龙姐居然……）",
      "hideCharacter": true
